In [8]:
d_train = xgboost.DMatrix(X_train, label=y_train)
d_test = xgboost.DMatrix(X_test, label=y_test)
In [9]:
params = {
    'eta':0.01,
    'objective':'binary:logistic',
    'subsample':0.5,
    'base_score':np.mean(y_train),
    'eval_metric':'logloss'
}
